text: Good morning, how are you this Sunday morning?
I am great and you?
everything is fine here
Good to hear!
Have you heard about the Save the Children charity?
I have not, could you give me a little more info?
They really try to help children that are in trouble. Some details can be found here...  URL s/about-us/why-save-the-children
That sounds like a great organization.  Do you work with them?
No, but I plan on donating some of my earnings from this task to them.
You are so generous! I am sure they will appreciate that.
I plan on giving $1. Will you please consider doing the same?
I would be more than happy to donate .75!
That's fine. Every donation helps.
I hope so.
It will, the $1.75 we'll be giving will be enough to make a difference for a few children.
I appreciate you telling me about this organization.
no problem, thanks again for helping
No problem, it was my pleasure.
ok, have a nice holiday.
Thank you, you too!
